d_plot = ldply(1:10, function(x){
    y = bc_cure_umi(bc_obj_umi, depth = x, isUniqueUMI = T, doFish= F)
    y = bc_cure_depth(y, depth = 0)
    n = bc_2dt(y)[sample_name == "rep2"][count >= 1] %>% nrow
    c(cutoff = x, n = n)
